name: keep moveing
description: this is my first time climbing a mountain. I don't know how to climb a mountain at all and I don't know the rules of climbing a mountain. At that time I was separated from the group. because it's too cool to take pictures. until finally it turned out that I chose the road around the mountain. and too late to drop back to the starting post. luckily I met other climbers who also took the same path as me.
